• Unauthorized remote access potential
• Network-level exposure via shared infrastructure
Operational Downtime: None
Data Loss: None
System Integrity: Fully verified
The overall security posture has been significantly strengthened.

Incident Context (Device-Specific)
Detection Source: Windows Security
